Package fr.unilim.javance.projet.internal

Interface Summary
TodoListener Listener on todo operations This listener must be implemented if you want to obtain notification on TodoManager operations.
TodoManager Todo management interface This interface must be implemented to use a specific backend.
 

Class Summary
Folder Collection of Tasks A Folder is a collection of Tasks (ie. a folder contains several tasks).
Task A task in a "todo" This class defines a task in the todo application implementation.
TodoManagerFactory Todo manager factory This factory aims to instantiate TodoManager objects corresponding to the required backend.
 

Enum Summary
Backend Backends enumeration This enumeration contains all named backend which are available through the TodoManagerFactory.
Priority Define task priorities.
